          Call or SMS your name, age, sex &amp; location to:
        %p
          %span.number
            2442
          E.x. 'im Mara girl 26 PP'
        %p.note
          * Smart &amp; Beeline customers only.
      %li.even
        %h5
          International (beta)
        %p
          For international users, SMS or call:
        %p
          %span.number
            +1 415-692-6280

